 10. SPARK DEPLOYMENT MODES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
 Client Mode  → Driver on client machine | Interactive/notebooks
              → If client fails → Job fails
              spark-submit --master yarn --deploy-mode client app.py

 Cluster Mode → Driver on cluster node | Production/batch jobs
              → Fault-tolerant after submission
              spark-submit --master yarn --deploy-mode cluster app.py

 Local Mode   → Driver + Executor on same machine | Dev/testing
              → local[*] = all cores | local[4] = 4 threads

