 KEY INTERVIEW POINTS – QUICK FIRE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
 ✔ Driver = brain | Executor = worker.
 ✔ Lazy eval = no execution until action triggered.
 ✔ Lineage = fault tolerance WITHOUT data replication.
 ✔ Immutable + Lineage = RESILIENT (RDD full form meaning).
 ✔ 1 Action = 1 Job → Stages (at shuffle) → Tasks (per partition).
 ✔ Wide transformation = shuffle = expensive = new Stage.
 ✔ Always use SparkSession (Spark 2.x+), never SparkContext directly.
 ✔ Catalyst Optimizer only works on DataFrame/Dataset, NOT RDD.
 ✔ cache() = MEMORY_ONLY | persist() = choose your storage level.
 ✔ Broadcast join = fastest | Sort Merge = default for large tables.
 ✔ Parquet = best for Spark | ORC = best for Hive | Avro = best for ETL.
 ✔ Snappy = fast but low compression | Gzip = slow but high compression.
 ✔ inferSchema = NOT for production (use explicit schema).
 ✔ coalesce = reduce partitions (no shuffle) | repartition = increase (shuffle).
 ✔ Execution OOM = task fails | Storage OOM = LRU eviction (no failure).
